name: Isolation
description: When hit with the ugly side of life. People will tend to shell up. They still have all the amazing traits within but the trauma caused has made them scared to show it off. These people need our help. They need encouragement and praise. Isolation helps to develop skills, but too much will make them dwindle without the proper support. The right motivation and help will make the isolation a place for knowledge building and introspective thought. Isolation makes people experience the real.
